  "description": "This MEG dataset contains recordings from a cognitive neuroscience study investigating planning, memory, and replay processes. The dataset includes trigger channels for event marking and timing, with approximately 20 ms delay between trigger signals and visual stimulus onset as measured by photodiode. Event files are provided for reference, though MEG triggers should be used for precise temporal analysis.",
  "methods_description": "Data were collected using MEG with trigger channels for event marking. Visual stimuli were presented via projector with timing delays estimated at approximately 20 ms between trigger signal and visual onset, as calibrated using a photodiode.",
